query:
SELECT
                DISTINCT ON (hashed_key) hashed_key,
                miniblock_number,
                value
            FROM
                storage_logs
            WHERE
                hashed_key = ANY ($1)
                AND miniblock_number <= $2
                AND miniblock_number <= COALESCE(
                    (
                        SELECT
                            MAX(number)
                        FROM
                            miniblocks
                    ),
                    (
                        SELECT
                            miniblock_number
                        FROM
                            snapshot_recovery
                    )
                )
            ORDER BY
                hashed_key,
                miniblock_number DESC,
                operation_number DESC
